data.title: Wayland Health Center
data.meta_description: Tri-County Family Medicine Program, Inc. In Dansville, NY Offers A Wide Range Of Medical Services For You And Your Family. We Provide Comprehensive Primary Care, Pediatrics, Geriatric Services, Family Medicine, Obstetrics, & More. Visit Our Wayland Health Center Page. Call (585) 335-3100 To Learn More!
data.text:
Our health center is not far from sparkling Loon Lake, a wildlife habitat and recreational area. At Wayland, we see patients at birth, as children and teens, into adulthood, and as they age. We consider it a great privilege to treat people in our community through all stages of their lives.

We also provide services regardless of your ability to pay. Ask us about our Sliding Fee Discount Program.

Call us for an appointment: (585) 728-5131.
